:01:35.000Z","msg":"HKD?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:14:44.000Z","msg":"Search 港蛋留英"},{"pid":"b818a5745d546af975e3de8c9043689cc468bb4b","tid":2346000,"uid":284932,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:39:26.000Z","msg":"樓豬一條友移民英國?我都有類似既經驗 <br />\n去英國有數得計 <br />\nBNO Visa (1月31日網上申請) <br />\n30 months BNO Visa: &pound;180<br />\n30 months Immigration Health Surcharge: &pound;1,560<br />\n照 Tuberculosis (英國參考價) &pound;220<br />\nTotal: &pound;1,960<br />\n <br />\n倫敦機票加一星期酒店 (可能要買家俬, 要裝 internet) <br />\nBA 倫敦單程機票約: &pound;440<br />\n倫敦一星期酒店約: &pound;260<br />\nTotal:  &pound;700<br />\n <br />\nOne-bedroom or studio apartment <br />\nEast London 預 &pound;700 至 &pound;950 pcm (每月) <br />\n請樓主自己上 <a href=\"http://rightmove.co.uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frightmove.co.uk&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=f224f69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">rightmove.co.uk</a> 搵 <br />\n當佢 &pound;900 一個月, 6個月要: &pound;5,400<br />\n <br />\n買家俬 (英國租 flat 包唔包家俬?) <br />\n如果唔包: <br />\nBed frame: &pound;30<br />\nMattress: &pound;99<br />\nTable:  &pound;16<br />\nChair: &pound;22<br />\nIKEA delivery &amp; installation (我估) &pound;200<br />\nTotal: &pound;367<br />\n <br />\n食, 住, 行 <br />\nGrocery (唔肯定&pound;300一個月夠唔夠) &pound;300x6: &pound;1,800<br />\nUtilities (水電上網, 當佢 &pound;300 一個月) &pound;300x6: &pound;1,800<br />\nLondon Monthly Travelcard (Zones 1&ndash;4) &pound;199x6 &pound;1,196<br />\n &pound;4,796<br />\n<br />\n我計到 6 個月既 Grand total for 倫敦 (未計 Council Tax): $13,222.80"},{"pid":"60e1c715c1bf6702c74d011c09a8db8674649952","tid":2346000,"uid":284932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:40:02.000Z","msg":"Sorry 係 GBP &pound;13,222.80"},{"pid":"72f84c52671f097a9a71078036368f65e680c322","tid":2346000,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2bff32504339e79663571b94bbc869ad8ed14529","tid":2346000,"uid":47466,"like":2,"dislike":